" Enabling auto-indent
filetype plugin indent on
filetype indent on

" Disable Arrow keys in Normal mode
map <up> <nop>
map <down> <nop>
map <left> <nop>
map <right> <nop>
map <Home> <nop>
map <End> <nop>
map <PageUp> <nop>
map <PageDown> <nop>

" Disable Arrow keys in Insert mode
imap <up> <nop>
imap <down> <nop>
imap <left> <nop>
imap <right> <nop>
imap <PageUp> <nop>
imap <PageDown> <nop>

